        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When it comes to subtle elegance, few accessories express individuality like a nose pin. It’s not just jewelry—it’s a reflection of personality, tradition, and modern beauty. But with so many designs available, how do you choose the right one? This guide explores <strong>which type of nose pin suits an oval face</strong> and how to pair it with Lucira Jewelry’s ethically crafted <strong>lab-grown diamond designs</strong> for a timeless yet conscious look.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding the Oval Face Shape",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding the Oval Face Shape</h2><p>An oval face is characterized by balanced proportions—a slightly narrower chin, high cheekbones, and a soft jawline. It’s often considered the most versatile face shape for jewelry because nearly every style complements its symmetry.</p><p>If you have an oval face, you’re lucky: you can experiment with a variety of nose pin designs, from delicate studs to statement hoops. The key is choosing a design that enhances your natural harmony without overpowering your features.</p>",
            "custom_id": "22carat"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Choosing the Right Nose Pin Matters",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Choosing the Right Nose Pin Matters</h2><p>A nose pin draws attention to the center of your face. The right design highlights your features, while the wrong one can disrupt balance. For an oval face, the goal is to maintain proportion—delicate, refined shapes that complement your natural flow.</p><p>When you’re choosing between metals or gemstones, consider your personal aesthetic and comfort. Whether you prefer a minimalist gold stud or a <strong>lab-grown diamond</strong> piece, the material should enhance both your look and your values.</p><p>Lucira Jewelry specializes in <strong>sustainable diamond jewelry</strong>, offering certified, conflict-free pieces that combine modern craftsmanship with ethical responsibility.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Which Type of Nose Pin Suits on Oval Face",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Which Type of Nose Pin Suits on Oval Face</h2><h3>1. Solitaire Diamond Nose Pin</h3><p>The simplicity of a single diamond complements the natural symmetry of an oval face. A <strong>solitaire nose pin</strong> adds just the right amount of sparkle without being overpowering. Choose a <strong>lab-grown diamond</strong> stud for a luxurious yet sustainable choice.</p><p>Lucira’s collection of<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-earrings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond earrings</span></a> also pairs beautifully with a solitaire nose pin for a cohesive, elegant look.</p><h3>2. Floral Nose Pin Design</h3><p>Soft floral patterns mirror the natural curves of an oval face. This design brings a feminine touch while maintaining balance. A floral nose pin in yellow gold or white gold with small diamonds can add sophistication to both everyday and festive looks.</p><h3>3. Hoop or Ring Nose Pin</h3><p>If you prefer a bohemian or contemporary edge, thin gold or diamond hoops are perfect for oval faces. The gentle curve of a ring accentuates the smooth contour of your face, giving it character and charm. Avoid oversized hoops—opt for delicate rings that sit close to the nostril for a balanced appeal.</p><h3>4. Teardrop or Drop-Shaped Nose Pin</h3><p>The teardrop shape enhances the natural length of an oval face, giving it a graceful elongation. This design works beautifully in <strong>lab-grown diamond</strong> settings, where the subtle sparkle catches light and draws attention softly.</p><h3>5. Gold Nose Stud with Diamond Accent</h3><p>This design blends traditional aesthetics with a touch of modern sparkle. A gold nose pin with a tiny lab-grown diamond offers versatility—perfect for everyday wear or special occasions.</p><p>You can complement this look with a delicate<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond necklace</span></a> to complete the set with effortless sophistication.</p>",
            "custom_id": "importance"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Common Mistakes to Avoid",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2><ul><li>Choosing oversized or angular designs that break facial symmetry.<br/></li><li>Ignoring your skin’s undertone when selecting metal color—cool tones look best with white gold, while warm tones pair beautifully with yellow gold.<br/></li><li>Neglecting balance when pairing with other jewelry—keep proportions in harmony.<br/></li><li>Not considering comfort; the right fit ensures both style and ease.</li></ul>",
            "custom_id": "components"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Ethical Elegance of Lab-Grown Diamonds",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Ethical Elegance of Lab-Grown Diamonds</h2><p>At Lucira Jewelry, every piece is a blend of artistry and responsibility. <strong>Lab-grown diamonds</strong> offer the same brilliance, hardness, and sparkle as mined diamonds—without the environmental impact.</p><p>Whether it’s a nose pin, a <strong>lab-grown diamond necklace</strong>, or a pair of<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/diamond-stud-earrings-on-ear\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">diamond stud earrings on ear</span></a>, Lucira’s creations celebrate conscious luxury.</p><p>For those curious about diamond value, explore the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/1-carat-lab-grown-diamond-price-in-india\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">1 carat lab grown diamond price in India</span></a> collection to understand how ethical beauty can be affordable and everlasting.</p>",
            "custom_id": "check"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rQKzCe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Comparing Gold Purities: Why Choose 22K Hallmarked Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Expert Styling Tips from Lucira Jewelry</h2><ul><li><strong>Minimalism is key:</strong> Pair your nose pin with subtle earrings for an understated glow.<br/></li><li><strong>Day to night transition:</strong> Opt for convertible or dual-tone designs that suit both casual and festive wear.<br/></li><li><strong>Balance your look:</strong> If your nose pin has a diamond accent, pair it with plain gold earrings or a sleek chain.<br/></li><li><strong>Quality over quantity:</strong> Always choose certified, IGI-approved lab-grown diamonds for assurance and brilliance.<br/></li></ul><p>“Your jewelry should feel like an extension of who you are—effortless, ethical, and eternal.”<br/> — Lucira Jewelry Design Team</p>",
            "custom_id": "comparison"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Find the Nose Pin That Complements You",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Find the Nose Pin That Complements You</h2><p>Choosing <strong>which type of nose pin suits on oval face</strong> is about enhancing what you already have—a naturally balanced shape that pairs beautifully with timeless designs. At Lucira Jewelry, every piece is crafted with precision and purpose, ensuring that you never have to choose between beauty and conscience.</p><p>Explore Lucira’s exquisite range of <strong>lab-grown diamond jewelry</strong>, from nose pins to necklaces and earrings, and experience the sparkle of modern luxury redefined.</p><p><strong>Discover your perfect match today.<br/></strong> Shop <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a> – where elegance meets ethics.</p>",
